Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback



























amerinst insurance group ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Insurance
Sub-Industry: Reinsurance
Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd. acts as a reinsurer of professional liability insurance policies that are issued under the Professional Liability Insurance Plan sponsored by the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants ("AICPA").




