On Tuesday, June 14, 2005,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        AMERINST by 
                        AmerInst Insurance Group, Ltd., Hamilton HM GX.
                        The USPTO has given the AMERINST 
                        trademark serial  number of  78650019.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for AMERINST is 
                        
                        
                                            Ryan P. Hiler of 
                                            Ice Miller LLP,  One American Square, Suite 2900, Indianapolis IN 46282 
                                .
                            The AMERINST trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for AMERINST 
                            is Insurance and financial services, namely, insurance underwriting of all types of insurance and insurance administration; providing information in insurance matters; insurance consultation; financial analysis and consultation; management of a capital investment fund; financial portfolio management; financial risk management; financial services in the nature of an investment security, namely, underwriting of securities; investment banking services, namely, administration and management of securities and derivative products. 
                            





