Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 23, 2017 8:59 AM ET
Insurance

Company Overview of Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
AmerInst Insurance Group, Ltd., through its subsidiaries, provides insurance solutions to professional service firms in the United States. It operates through two segments, Reinsurance Activity and Insurance Activity. The company engages in the reinsurance of professional liability insurance for certified public accountants and attorneys, as well as investments and other activities. AmerInst Insurance Group, Ltd. was founded in 1998 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda.


Continental BuildingPO Box HM 160125 Church StreetHamilton,  HM GXBermudaFounded in 199825 Employees



Phone: 441-295-6015

Fax: 441-295-1702

www.amerinst.bm







