Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd. Key Developments

Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd Ratifies the Appointment of Deloitte & Touche Ltd as an Independent Auditor
Jun 6 17
Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd. announced at the AGM held on June 01, 2017, the shareholders ratified the appointment of Deloitte & Touche Ltd. as an independent auditors for fiscal year ending December 31, 2017.


Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd. Announces Dividend Payable on or About June 15, 2017
Jun 6 17
Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd. declared a dividend of $0.50 per share, to be paid on or about June 15, 2017 to shareholders of record as of May 31, 2017.


Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd., Annual General Meeting, Jun 01, 2017
Apr 26 17
Amerinst Insurance Group Ltd., Annual General Meeting, Jun 01, 2017, at 10:00 Atlantic Standard Time. Agenda: To consider and act upon the nomination of each of Irvin F. Diamond, Jeffry I. Gillman and David R. Klunk for election as a director with a three-year term; to ratify the appointment of Deloitte Ltd. as independent auditor for fiscal year 2017; and to transact such other business as may properly come before the Annual General Meeting or any adjournment thereof.


