Company Description                    




                        AmerInst Insurance Group, Ltd. is an insurance holding company with four subsidiaries: AmerInst Insurance Company, Ltd., AmerInst Investment Company, Ltd., AmerInst Mezco, Ltd. and AmerInst Professional Services, Ltd. It is engaged in providing reinsurance services of professional liability insurance policies and portfolio management of fixed-income securities through its subsidiaries.                    


